<div class="main_pic">
<img src="safety1.png" alt="Purdue Fire Station">
</div>
<div class="intro">
<p>All Residence Halls are equipped with up-to-date safety equipment. To the left is a chart with the given Fire Protective Systems that each Residence Hall is provided with. Along with the safety equipment, Purdue University has two Fire Stations on campus with around-the-clock staff.</p>
<br />
<p>Purdue's Campus also has Emergency Telephone Call Boxes indicated by a bright blue light placed in strategic locations. Each box is a direct line to the Purdue Police and sends a location of where the call came from. Walking at night after a study session is now safer than ever.</p>
</div>
